2. cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the performance metrics of interest in wireless communication systems, which is a topic of interest in networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the analysis of wireless communication channels, which is a subfield of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the analysis of a specific model for wireless communication channels, which can be seen as a system, and the analysis of its performance metrics, which is a topic of interest in systems and control. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - Although less likely, the paper could be relevant to multiagent systems as it deals with the analysis of wireless communication channels, which can be seen as a network of agents communicating with each other.
